        html:Face="Arial" x:Family="Swiss"> The unit used to specify the time between each billing point in the schedule.  Used in conjunction with the recurring multiplier to determine the total time span of the product service schedule.  FK_UNT_REC_PER_ID (Type: String, Length: 15) </Font></ss:Data></Comment></Cell>
